{"id":"RUIHE4","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["幸運の鶴\n\n<size=45>その四  瑞鶴と大先輩<\/size>",1]]},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"bgm":"battle-1","say":"夕方・演習海域","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","say":"良いぞ！その調子で攻撃してこい！","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","say":"はい！","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":307060,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/plane","bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","side":2,"dir":1,"say":"瑞鶴の艦載機が投下した模擬弾が見事に三笠を直撃。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","say":"あいた！","nameColor":"#a9f548","action":[{"y":0,"x":15,"dur":0.1,"number":3,"type":"shake"}],"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","say":"勝負あり！…って三笠大先輩！大丈夫ですかー！","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":307060,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","say":"う、うむ…それより、見事な爆撃だ！特訓を始めた頃と比べると素晴らしい進歩だぞ！","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305110,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","say":"ありがとうございます！…指揮官、今のどうだ！","nameColor":"#a9f548","action":[{"y":30,"type":"shake","number":3,"dur":0.15}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","say":"…あははは！いいよいいよ別にそんなに褒めなくても～！よし、これで「グレイゴースト」に一歩近づけたはず！","nameCol